{"tid":156311,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"騙案？Finders全球專業代購美日集運","createTime":"2017-03-14T15:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T11:19:57.000Z","uid":12228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47158a40488c701582691ece743a425235828456","tid":156311,"uid":12228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T15:36:28.000Z","msg":"騙案？Finders全球專業代購美日集運<br />\n想問下有冇人係呢間野到買過野？<br />\n我2月3號巳經過左數訂一隻Dw手錶$650<br />\n但係3月7號佢地先再話我知件貨寄失左，咁我簡退錢，佢話10號會過反數比我，但我到今日都收唔到退款<br />\n呢間野仆街到，成撚日唔覆機，今日whatsapp佢聽日都未必覆你<br />\n<br />\n地址:荃灣華力工業中心 15 樓 G 室荃灣柴灣角青山公路荃灣段 459 號 ( 愉景新城鈄對面 / 消防局正門右手邊 ) <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TP374UA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTP374UA.jpg&h=bc9f994c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce4738817596a31562ecfe119bba6614daf0ba25","tid":156311,"uid":12228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T15:41:12.000Z","msg":"我想問我可以點做？<br />\n650$其實唔多<br />\n但條氣好撚唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個重點係話呢家落單14號前有機會到<br />\n不個我諗係下個月14號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/14/234104_909f1800331884a5f2dab57786d9d279.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F14%2F234104_909f1800331884a5f2dab57786d9d279.jpg&h=114a0b63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49ad65d219455987b9b3e49fc4265ddbfdccee72","tid":156311,"uid":12228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T15:48:38.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"853b76fd5c5d8baf7d0a70ac2378b829e70f4d74","tid":156311,"uid":12228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T15:51:15.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"c102934a2579d846e48d315eb17dfcde9b986caa","tid":156311,"uid":12228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:52:37.000